HEADWORD: Circumcursation
<hw>Cir`cum*cur*sa"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>circumcursare</ets>, <ets>-satum</ets>, to run round about.]</ety>
<def>The act of running about; also, rambling language.</def>
